    dc:description "FIGURES 90–92. Macratria sentani sp. nov., holotype ♁. 90—Habitus, dorsal view; 91—Same, head (dorsal view) and pronotum (lateral view); 92—Left metatibia, dorsal view [not to scale]." ;
